      *              * Preparazione file area generica                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "had "               to   f-xxx-nam              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione pathname modulo oggetto            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "tpg/gct/fls/ioc/obj/iofhad"
                                          to   f-xxx-obj              .
