      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      low-values           to   had-k01                .
           start     had    key not less
                            had-k01
                            invalid key
                            go to exe-cnv-had-800.
       exe-cnv-had-250.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Next su [old-had]                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
