           move      had-alx-exp          to   rf-had-alx-exp         .
       exe-cnv-had-700.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Scrittura [new-had]                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "PT"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      f-xxx-obj            to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-had                 .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se errore : no incremento records scritti       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to exe-cnv-had-750.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento numero records scritti               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   inc-rec-scr-000      thru inc-rec-scr-999        .
       exe-cnv-had-750.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo a Next                                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-cnv-had-250.
       exe-cnv-had-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Close files                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Close file [old-had]                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           close     had                                              .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Close file [new-had]                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "CL"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      f-xxx-obj            to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-had                 .
       exe-cnv-had-850.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione nr records letti e scritti      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-rec-let-000      thru vis-rec-let-999        .
           perform   vis-rec-scr-000      thru vis-rec-scr-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione presa visione                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
